DESCRIPTIVE SUMMARY

Title:
National Association of Manufactures Pamphlets, 1945-1969
Repository:
Kheel Center for Labor-Management Documentation & Archives
Collection Number:
5340
Abstract:
Tracts and pamphlets on topics related to the labor question and the free enterprise system. Also included are a sample of NAM periodical literature and releases of the NAM Press Bureau.
Creator:
National Association of Manufactures (NAM)
Quanitities:
3 cubic feet
Language:
Collection material in English
Tracts and pamphlets on topics related to the labor question and the free enterprise system. Also included are a sample of NAM periodical literature and releases of the NAM Press Bureau.
Access to the collections in the Kheel Center is restricted. Please contact a reference archivist for access to these materials.
Conditions Governing Use

This collection must be used in keeping with the Kheel Center Information Sheet and Procedures for Document Use.
INFORMATION FOR USERS
Preferred Citation

National Association of Manufactures Pamphlets #5340. Kheel Center for Labor-Management Documentation and Archives, Cornell University Library.
